	71. How to change image size without distortion?
	To change image size without distortion, we maintain the aspect ratio.
	Best ways:
		â€¢ Use width and height: auto
		â€¢ Use object-fit: cover or contain
	Example:
	
	img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}
	or
	
	img {
  width: 300px;
  height: 200px;
  object-fit: cover;
}
	One-line interview answer:
		To avoid distortion, we maintain aspect ratio using height auto or object-fit.
	
	72. How to create a responsive navbar?
