	73. Why Flexbox is better than float?
	Flexbox is better because:
		â€¢ Easy alignment (center, spacing)
		â€¢ Responsive by default
		â€¢ Less CSS code
		â€¢ No clearfix issues
	Float problems:
		â€¢ Not designed for layout
		â€¢ Needs clear fixes
	One-line interview answer:
		Flexbox is better than float because it provides easy alignment and responsive layouts.
		71. When to use Grid vs Flexbox?
			â€¢ Use Flexbox for one-dimensional layouts (row or column)
ðŸ‘‰ navigation bars, buttons, cards alignment
			â€¢ Use Grid for two-dimensional layouts (rows and columns)
ðŸ‘‰ full page layout, dashboard, gallery
		One-line interview answer:
